---

<Base title={`${title} | 易經研究所`} description={description} canonical={`${site}/articles/eight-trigrams-guide`} keywords="八卦,乾坤震巽坎離艮兌,八卦入門,八卦象徵,先天八卦,後天八卦" schema={schema} ogType="article" ogImage="https://yijin.builtbyclaw.com/articles/hero/article-eight-trigrams.webp" articleSection="卦象解析" activePage="articles">

